{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-0-10-46-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Design Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/components","title":{"zh":"图表组件设计指引","en":"Design for Components of Charts"},"order":1}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>图例解释了图表区域中包含的所有视觉元素的含义。</p>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>对图表中的图形进行解释说明，用来<strong>映射图形的尺寸、颜色、数值大小</strong>等含义，帮助用户直观地理解图表。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>由映射图形形状 + 文本组成。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*cuBUSJcvI9IAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<h2 id=\"类型\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>根据数据类型不同，分为<strong>连续型图例</strong>和<strong>分类型图例</strong>。<br />根据状态不同，图例可以被设置为<strong>静态</strong>或可<strong>交互态</strong>。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*2lZfQYFzLfYAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"问题-1：如何决定图例的位置？\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 1：如何决定图例的位置？ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 1：如何决定图例的位置？</h3>\n<p>图例是对图形本身的概括。通常人的视觉动线是从上至下，从左到右。默认把图例放在左上角去做一个通用的方案看起来没毛病。<br />但更好的做法是：<strong>缩短用户对照图例看图形的本能路径，提升信息获取效率。</strong><br /><strong><br /></strong><br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*mE-5QbrfhNsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/><br /><strong><br />虽然图例的位置从技术上支持了 12 个位置，我们总结了图例在不同的图表类型中不同的位置后，经过克制收敛为两类，并应用在 plot 图表类库中，以及智能生成图表工具中。<br /></strong>设计者和观看者甚至并不会感知到位置的变化，但是对应图形获取信息的效率就在不经意间提升了。<strong><br /></strong><br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*uuHERrMiBTUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=500/></p>\n<h3 id=\"问题-2：图例太多怎么办？\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-2%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 2：图例太多怎么办？ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 2：图例太多怎么办？</h3>\n<p>在 g2plot 中，图例如果占据了图表大部分的位置，你可以发现我们提供了翻页功能。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">何时使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\">元素</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">类型</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">常见问题</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9F\">问题 1：如何决定图例的位置？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/legend/#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-2%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\">问题 2：图例太多怎么办？</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":15600.000000000002}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"specification/components/legend.en.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"色板","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter"